snippet.title: Formula Funtico Annoucement Trailer
snippet.description:
Formula Funtico is a competitive multiplayer racing game that will take you on a wild ride across a vibrant multiverse. Inspired by arcade classics, Formula Funtico is all about high-octane action, strategic power-ups, and neck-and-neck finishes.
